{
  "uid": "assistant-observability",
  "title": "Assistant Observability",
  "schemaVersion": 41,
  "version": 1,
  "refresh": "15s",
  "time": {"from": "now-1h", "to": "now"},
  "panels": [
    {"id":16,"type":"text","title":"Dashboard guide","gridPos":{"x":0,"y":0,"w":24,"h":4},"options":{"mode":"markdown","content":"**p95**는 요청 100건을 빠른 순서로 나열했을 때 95번째 요청이 걸린 시간입니다. p95가 3초라면 요청 100건 중 약 95건은 3초 안에 끝났고, 약 5건은 더 오래 걸렸다는 뜻입니다."}},
    {"id":1,"type":"row","title":"Service","gridPos":{"x":0,"y":4,"w":24,"h":1}},
    {"id":2,"type":"stat","title":"Monitoring status","description":"애플리케이션과 데이터베이스의 관측 데이터를 받을 수 있는 상태입니다. `1`은 모두 수집 가능, `0`은 하나 이상 수집 불가를 뜻합니다.","gridPos":{"x":0,"y":5,"w":6,"h":8},"datasource":{"uid":"prometheus","type":"prometheus"},"targets":[{"refId":"A","expr":"min(up{job=~\"my-ai-assistant|postgres\"})"}],"fieldConfig":{"defaults":{"unit":"none"}}},
    {"id":3,"type":"timeseries","title":"Request rate","description":"서비스가 받는 HTTP API 요청의 초당 평균 수입니다.","gridPos":{"x":6,"y":5,"w":6,"h":8},"datasource":{"uid":"prometheus","type":"prometheus"},"targets":[{"refId":"A","expr":"sum(rate(http_requests_total{job=\"my-ai-assistant\"}[5m])) or vector(0)"}],"fieldConfig":{"defaults":{"unit":"reqps"}}},
    {"id":4,"type":"timeseries","title":"Error rate","description":"서버 오류(5xx)로 끝난 HTTP API 요청의 비율입니다.","gridPos":{"x":12,"y":5,"w":6,"h":8},"datasource":{"uid":"prometheus","type":"prometheus"},"targets":[{"refId":"A","expr":"(100 * sum(rate(http_requests_total{job=\"my-ai-assistant\",status=~\"5..\"}[5m])) / clamp_min(sum(rate(http_requests_total{job=\"my-ai-assistant\"}[5m])), 1e-9)) or vector(0)"}],"fieldConfig":{"defaults":{"unit":"percent"}}},
    {"id":5,"type":"timeseries","title":"HTTP request duration p95","description":"스트리밍 메시지를 제외한 HTTP API 요청이 완료되기까지 걸린 시간입니다.","gridPos":{"x":18,"y":5,"w":6,"h":8},"datasource":{"uid":"prometheus","type":"prometheus"},"targets":[{"refId":"A","expr":"histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (le) (rate(http_request_duration_seconds_bucket{job=\"my-ai-assistant\",path!=\"/api/conversations/{conversation_id}/messages\"}[5m])))"}],"fieldConfig":{"defaults":{"unit":"s"}}},
    {"id":6,"type":"row","title":"Model","gridPos":{"x":0,"y":13,"w":24,"h":1}},
    {"id":7,"type":"timeseries","title":"Model response start time p95","description":"모델이 요청을 받은 뒤 답변을 시작하기까지 걸린 시간입니다.","gridPos":{"x":0,"y":14,"w":6,"h":8},"datasource":{"uid":"prometheus","type":"prometheus"},"targets":[{"refId":"A","expr":"histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (le) (rate(llm_first_token_seconds_bucket{job=\"my-ai-assistant\"}[5m])))"}],"fieldConfig":{"defaults":{"unit":"s"}}},
    {"id":8,"type":"timeseries","title":"Model response completion time p95","description":"모델이 요청을 받은 뒤 답변을 완료하기까지 걸린 시간입니다.","gridPos":{"x":6,"y":14,"w":6,"h":8},"datasource":{"uid":"prometheus","type":"prometheus"},"targets":[{"refId":"A","expr":"histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (le) (rate(llm_stream_duration_seconds_bucket{job=\"my-ai-assistant\"}[5m])))"}],"fieldConfig":{"defaults":{"unit":"s"}}},
    {"id":9,"type":"timeseries","title":"Model response failure rate","description":"모델이 요청을 처리하는 동안 실패한 횟수입니다.","gridPos":{"x":12,"y":14,"w":6,"h":8},"datasource":{"uid":"prometheus","type":"prometheus"},"targets":[{"refId":"A","expr":"sum(rate(llm_stream_failures_total{job=\"my-ai-assistant\"}[5m]))"}],"fieldConfig":{"defaults":{"unit":"ops"}}},
    {"id":11,"type":"row","title":"Database","gridPos":{"x":0,"y":22,"w":24,"h":1}},
    {"id":12,"type":"stat","title":"DB pool in use","description":"애플리케이션이 현재 사용 중인 DB 연결 수입니다.","gridPos":{"x":0,"y":23,"w":6,"h":8},"datasource":{"uid":"prometheus","type":"prometheus"},"targets":[{"refId":"A","expr":"db_pool_in_use{job=\"my-ai-assistant\"}"}],"fieldConfig":{"defaults":{"unit":"none"}}},
    {"id":13,"type":"timeseries","title":"Lock conflict rate","description":"같은 대화에 쓰기 요청이 동시에 들어와 거절된 횟수입니다.","gridPos":{"x":6,"y":23,"w":6,"h":8},"datasource":{"uid":"prometheus","type":"prometheus"},"targets":[{"refId":"A","expr":"sum(rate(conversation_lock_conflicts_total{job=\"my-ai-assistant\"}[5m]))"}],"fieldConfig":{"defaults":{"unit":"ops"}}},
    {"id":14,"type":"stat","title":"PostgreSQL connections","description":"선택한 PostgreSQL 데이터베이스에 현재 열려 있는 연결 수입니다.","gridPos":{"x":12,"y":23,"w":6,"h":8},"datasource":{"uid":"prometheus","type":"prometheus"},"targets":[{"refId":"A","expr":"sum(pg_stat_database_numbackends{job=\"postgres\",datname=~\"$database\"})"}],"fieldConfig":{"defaults":{"unit":"none"}}},
    {"id":15,"type":"timeseries","title":"PostgreSQL cache hit ratio","description":"PostgreSQL이 데이터를 읽을 때 메모리 캐시에서 찾은 비율입니다.","gridPos":{"x":18,"y":23,"w":6,"h":8},"datasource":{"uid":"prometheus","type":"prometheus"},"targets":[{"refId":"A","expr":"100 * sum(rate(pg_stat_database_blks_hit{job=\"postgres\",datname=~\"$database\"}[5m])) / clamp_min(sum(rate(pg_stat_database_blks_hit{job=\"postgres\",datname=~\"$database\"}[5m])) + sum(rate(pg_stat_database_blks_read{job=\"postgres\",datname=~\"$database\"}[5m])), 1e-9)"}],"fieldConfig":{"defaults":{"unit":"percent"}}},
    {"id":17,"type":"row","title":"Tool","gridPos":{"x":0,"y":31,"w":24,"h":1}},
    {"id":18,"type":"timeseries","title":"Tool call rate by outcome","description":"모델용 도구를 호출한 초당 횟수입니다. outcome은 success, failed, timeout, denied처럼 고정된 결과 분류입니다.","gridPos":{"x":0,"y":32,"w":8,"h":8},"datasource":{"uid":"prometheus","type":"prometheus"},"targets":[{"refId":"A","expr":"sum by (tool_name, outcome) (rate(agent_tool_calls_total{job=\"my-ai-assistant\"}[5m])) or vector(0)"}],"fieldConfig":{"defaults":{"unit":"ops"}}},
    {"id":19,"type":"timeseries","title":"Tool call duration p95","description":"도구별 호출 시간의 p95입니다. 느린 외부 의존성이나 재시도를 평균 대신 상위 지연 시간으로 확인합니다.","gridPos":{"x":8,"y":32,"w":8,"h":8},"datasource":{"uid":"prometheus","type":"prometheus"},"targets":[{"refId":"A","expr":"histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (le, tool_name) (rate(agent_tool_duration_seconds_bucket{job=\"my-ai-assistant\"}[5m])))"}],"fieldConfig":{"defaults":{"unit":"s"}}},
    {"id":20,"type":"timeseries","title":"Tool call limit exceeded rate","description":"한 agent run에서 허용된 도구 호출 수를 초과해 중단된 초당 횟수입니다. 이 값이 지속되면 도구 설명이나 작업 분해를 점검합니다.","gridPos":{"x":16,"y":32,"w":8,"h":8},"datasource":{"uid":"prometheus","type":"prometheus"},"targets":[{"refId":"A","expr":"sum(rate(tool_calls_limit_exceeded_total{job=\"my-ai-assistant\"}[5m])) or vector(0)"}],"fieldConfig":{"defaults":{"unit":"ops"}}},
    {"id":21,"type":"stat","title":"Toolset availability","description":"애플리케이션 시작 시 각 MCP 도구 집합이 활성화되었는지 나타냅니다. `1`은 활성화됨, `0`은 활성화 실패를 뜻합니다.","gridPos":{"x":0,"y":40,"w":24,"h":8},"datasource":{"uid":"prometheus","type":"prometheus"},"targets":[{"refId":"A","expr":"mcp_toolset_up{job=\"my-ai-assistant\"}"}],"fieldConfig":{"defaults":{"unit":"none"}}}
  ],
  "templating": {
